org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor

Class ChainedBundleProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor.ChainedBundleProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BundleProcessor, Lifecycle

    public class ChainedBundleProcessor
extends Object
implements BundleProcessor
    A bundle processor chaining others processor. It composes the extender mechanism.

    Instance must be created using the create(org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.BundleProcessor...) method.

    • Field Detail

      • m_processors

        private final List<BundleProcessor> m_processors
        The list of processors. Be aware that the order if important, as processors will be called in the insertion order.

        Once the chained bundle processor is created, this list cannot be modified.
